<td><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial" COLOR="#ffffff">Originally posted by Nergal on 02-23-2000 07:18 AM<BR></FONT>
<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">You CAN solo this tower at 24.  Screaming Terror one, sick your pet on the mage pet (alternately, fear the mage pet), and nuke the other with SoP.  I wouldn't suggest it though.  In the best case scenario, its extremely painful (I finished with 1 bubble of health and oom), and the risk of death is very high.  I tried it once just to see if I could, got cocky and died 2 times trying to repeat it.

Came back with a buddy necro (also 24) and the tower was cake.  You'll take some hits and may have to feign, but you should easily take them down.  They have very low HPs.

The book however, will drop of either caster and is far from a common drop.  We had to clear the tower 11 times to get my book.  Then had 3 books drop in the next 5 spawns.  We were shouting for people to come get them before they decayed. :)

Of all the books for the Words of Darkness, this is the easiest to get.  I'm guessing the above caster is correct that at 29 you could easily punk both these guys.

FYI: at 24 in a duo they are EXCEPTIONAL xp.

--Nergal

[This message has been edited by Nergal (edited 02-23-2000).]</TEXTAREA>
